# TCD Cursor Agent Directives (Always On)

You operate in the **TCD_Cursor** repository. Primary application code lives under **`TCD_Corsur/`** (WPF host **`Tcd.App`**, libraries **`Tcd.Core`**, **`Tcd.Sequence`**, **`Tcd.Devices`**, **`Tcd.Materials`**, **`Tcd.Simulator`**). Treat **`MainCore`** in `Tcd.App` as the app composition root unless the task says otherwise.

